Comment: 1,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Takagisan - text_cn,,0,0,0,,——CN——
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,扳手腕
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.45,0:01:39.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么西片那么强啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我每天都做俯卧撑啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一天大概做几个啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.63,0:01:59.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,当天被高木同学捉弄次数的三倍
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.76,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说得出口啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 就随便做做啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,看当天的状态
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来和我比比吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.23,0:02:14.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你真的很强啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来赢他
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.59,0:02:36.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,又被留下来打扫卫生了？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.93,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,这还不是你害的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片 你这小子
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有什么事吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片 你把椅子搬过来一下
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.49,0:03:06.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么回事啊 高木同学…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要比一比吗 扳手腕
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很强 可以哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那输了的要请客喝果汁哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学 你不知道我扳手腕很厉害吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直坚持在做被你捉弄次数乘以三倍的俯卧撑
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,男生里面都没几个人能赢我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你就好好尝尝至今为止捉弄我的报应吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那开始吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚才牵手了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是觉得牵手很害羞吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.72,0:04:13.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好软 简直吹弹可破
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一捏就会坏掉的纤细感
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子的手吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.82,0:04:24.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你手心出汗了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是在紧张
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我都不介意啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能紧张啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再胡思乱想了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那开始了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.42,0:04:43.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这么弱的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是我变得太强了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太高兴了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学为了赢我竟然这么拼命啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我赢啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了…一不小心就得意忘形了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这场比赛我明明能赢的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个傻子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要再比一次吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.31,0:05:40.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以为同样的手段能奏效两次
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学 天真
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要一开始就用全力
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识见识我的臂力吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.75,0:06:00.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不如牵着手回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.25,0:06:03.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.01,0:06:06.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 开始
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,又是我赢了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要再来一次吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 算了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我帮你一起打扫
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧扫完回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然输给这么纤细的小手
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,黑板西片来擦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我去倒垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,回去请我喝果汁哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.33,0:07:18.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦 早苗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想事情啦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到初二了 要稍微成熟一点了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.42,0:07:28.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,初一初二都没什么区别吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.60,0:07:41.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,前段时间那么漂亮的樱花都凋谢了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,花的生命真是转瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不只有花是这样哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界的所有事物
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.57,0:07:56.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,全都 全都 全都是转瞬即逝的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.16,0:07:57.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说 没错
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多好吃的蛋糕都是有保质期的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,糖也是舔着舔着就没有了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是香蕉 放久了也会发黑变质
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是食物…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界的所有事物都是既有始也有终的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,青春终有一天也会结束
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 成熟完全不是这样的好嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.54,0:08:48.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都像是闹情绪的小孩啊 对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在开什么玩笑…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 很成熟 很成熟哦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真的真的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,美奈真的很成熟呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.61,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.36,0:09:10.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是孩子气
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,苦涩
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你可真有意思啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片 说好了要请我喝果汁的对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你决定好了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是多好喝的果汁
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.56,0:09:51.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,现在喝的果汁也只能尝到扳手腕输给高木同学的滋味
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.37,0:09:59.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.03,0:10:01.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喝什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我想喝这个
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我有件事想问你们
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟到底是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你是喜欢上北条同学了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.35,0:10:33.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很有名啊 她喜欢成熟的人这件事
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢成熟的人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个没关系啦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是好奇成熟到底是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.00,0:10:47.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只要具备这个
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就不会被高木同学捉弄了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.96,0:10:51.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片也喜欢上北条同学了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 西片喜欢的是高木同学吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 完全不是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 说起成熟
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是那个吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 告诉我吧 木村
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个当然是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  那个是咖啡哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.20,0:11:27.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 感觉今天就想喝这个
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的能喝吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你不是喝不了苦的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你也只有现在能这么说了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早上我都有喝妈妈煮的咖啡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.42,0:11:42.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不好喝 但也不是喝不了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,畏惧我的成熟吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,以后别再捉弄我了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.89,0:11:50.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且味道还这么浓
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然喝不了苦的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊 真好喝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉…怎么说呢 人都变精神了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不接着喝了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.45,0:12:07.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 西片 你是不是出手汗了？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有 这是附在罐子上的水滴啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这么说起来
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我有在网上看到过「正确的咖啡品尝方法」哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在嘴里稍微含着一会的话
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就能充分感受到咖啡的味道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 要把这种东西暂时留在嘴里？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我有看到过这种谣言呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 你也就只有现在能像这样来捉弄我了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快屈服在能喝光咖啡的我之下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这么难咽下去的话明明不用买的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 很好喝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学也喝喝看吧 约好我请你的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,选你喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.09,0:13:04.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要选什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这个
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜…蜜瓜苏打
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好喝
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我换着喝吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我喜欢喝咖啡
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是喝光了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头都麻了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 怎么样啊高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝一口蜜瓜苏打吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是…好想喝
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好想喝甜的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…我就恭敬不如从命…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是间接接吻
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 果然还是…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是再享受一下咖啡的余韵吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.18,0:14:33.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得就算能喝下咖啡也不算成熟哦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早就被她看穿了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算西片变成熟了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会努力捉弄你的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.28,0:14:54.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 等…真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,别在这种方面努力啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 笑什么笑啦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,自行车
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天真是太惨了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能不能有什么方法赢过高木同学呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.18,0:15:53.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 早上好 高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 感觉和平常不太一样
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么没骑自行车？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.15,0:16:12.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想和西片手牵手去上学 所以没骑过来
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这么想的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一见面就捉弄我
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样肯定能行
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我的自行车…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下 要是我能猜中你今天没骑自行车来的理由
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我赢了 怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天回家路上你随口说出的那句话
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉刹车不太灵了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没听漏哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这么轻松就赢了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点扫兴呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就是刹…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,猜错了的那一刻就是西片输了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.29,0:17:05.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等一会再告诉你
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.17,0:17:11.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要走这边试试吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以啦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.98,0:18:14.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,台阶 如果骑自行车的话就上不了台阶
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是为了走这条路？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是这样了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.24,0:18:20.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.09,0:18:38.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要慎重点 再思考一下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.30,0:18:44.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有自行车就能走和平常不一样的路上学了 好开心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.02,0:18:54.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路上常有附近的孩子们在地上画画哦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.86,0:18:56.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 有了有了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,来玩跳格子吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一一 二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一二一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.30,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一二一二一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学也还是个小孩子呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有自行车就能玩跳格子了 真开心呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学已经预料到这里有跳格子的涂鸦了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有自行车的话她自己就能玩耍了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.15,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 我不能着急
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,猜错就输了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.74,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.20,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要深思熟虑才行
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.49,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.16,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学 我感觉这场比赛不公平啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.87,0:19:51.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.96,0:19:57.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为就算我猜对了 只要你说猜错我就输了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.88,0:20:02.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的哦 我不会对西片你说谎的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是猫啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也有哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路上有很多猫的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,来 来 怎么样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学 我可以说答案了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你请
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.78,0:20:29.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你不是骑自行车而是走路上学的理由
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,刹车故障了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.54,0:20:38.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,台阶 跳格子游戏 然后还有猫
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.67,0:20:43.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是想让我觉得这些都是骑车做不到的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但似乎有点太刻意了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.14,0:20:53.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我的注意点离开你昨天不经意说出的刹车的违和感上
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的已经暴露无遗了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答对了还是答错了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.36,0:20:59.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答错了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.78,0:21:09.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是想要看到想猜中我为什么没有骑自行车
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.87,0:21:13.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因此而各种苦恼的西片呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 是西片你输了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.30,0:21:24.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在我发起挑战的时候就已经…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾啊 明明我准备了两个答案
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.26,0:21:32.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,两个？两个是指还有其他正确答案吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.43,0:21:32.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个答案是什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得西片你猜不到哦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,反正西片已经输了 无所谓啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 告诉我啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我最开始就告诉你了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.42,0:22:00.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我啦西片同学
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能没什么的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是没什么啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,——JP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,腕ずもう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:39.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 なんで そんなに強いんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあ 毎日 腕立てをやってるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,1日何回くらい  やってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:59.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,その日   高木さんに  からかわれた回数×3回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.76,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんて言えるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあ 適当だね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,その日のコンディションに  よるっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おい 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,次は俺とやろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:14.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホント強いな 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺が勝ってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:36.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,また居残り掃除?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.93,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,誰のせいだと思ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 こら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.02,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,す… すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な… 何か用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何してんの  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 イス持ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:06.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.58,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どういうこと  高木…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,勝負しない  腕ずもう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あんまり強くないけど いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 負けたほうが  ジュースおごるってことで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん  俺が腕ずもう強いことを  知らないんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,からかわれた回数×3回の腕立てを  やってきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,男子でも 俺に勝てるヤツは  ほとんどいないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今まで俺を からかってきた報いを  受けるがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 始めようか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,手 つないだよね さっき
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,い… いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もしかして  手つなぐの恥ずかしいの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.05,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ち… 違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:13.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,や… 柔らかい  フニフニしている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この頼りない骨の細工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.61,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,女の子の… 手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:24.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,手汗かいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.41,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もしかして緊張してる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,別に気にしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,き… 緊張なんて  するわけないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう余計なことは考えるな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ いくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,用意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:43.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ドン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何だ  この弱さは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺が強くなりすぎてしまったのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんて楽しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.29,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんが 俺に勝とうと  必死じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.55,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やった  勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.85,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,油断してしまった  つい楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,勝てる勝負だったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺のバカ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう1回やる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:40.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ぜひ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,2度も あんな手が通用すると  思っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ 甘い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,甘すぎるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,最初から全力でいく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.29,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺の筋力を食らえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:00.21,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.05,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,手つないで帰ろっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:03.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,は?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な… 何を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:06.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,用意 ドン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.52,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,また私の勝ちだね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう1回する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,, いや いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,さてと  掃除 手伝うから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,早く終わらせて帰ろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.29,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こんな細い手に負けるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,黒板は西片担当ね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私はゴミ捨ててくる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,帰り ジュースおごってね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.31,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうしたの  何かあった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  別に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.58,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いたたた…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何かあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:18.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,痛いよ サナエちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっと物思いにふけってみたの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう中2だし 大人っぽく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:28.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,はあ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,中1も中2も変わらないと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:41.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,つい こないだまで あんなに きれいだった桜の花も  散っちゃったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,花って はかないなって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,でも それは花だけじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この世界のあらゆるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:56.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,みんな みんな み〜んな はかない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,例えば?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:57.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,例えば?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.50,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,た… 例えば… そう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どんなに おいしいケーキにだって  賞味期限があるし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,アメも なめてるうちに  なくなってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,バナナだって  放っとくと黒ずんできちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,全部 食べ物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この世の全てには  始まりがあって 終わりがあるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.85,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,青春だって いつかは終わっちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いやいや  大人っぽくって  全然 そんな感じしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:48.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どう見ても  ご機嫌斜めな子供だって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,一体 何の冗談…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,い… いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 大人っぽい  大人っぽかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.27,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん ホント ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや ミナはホント大人っぽいな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントにホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホント ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.61,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,ねえ ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:10.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,子供
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,にがみ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.50,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片ってホント面白いねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片　ジュースおごってくれる  約束だったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっ うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何にしよっかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片は決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.19,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どんなに おいしくても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:51.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今飲むジュースは  高木さんに  腕ずもうで負けた敗北の味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:09:59.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:01.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何にしよっかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 違うな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日は これの気分だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なあ ちょっと聞きたいんだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.43,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽいって 何だと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,北条さん狙ってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:33.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だって 有名だぜ  タイプは大人っぽい人だ”って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私 大人っぽい人が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 関係ねえから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽいって何なのか  気になっただけだっての
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽさか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:47.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それがあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんに  からかわれなくなるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:51.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺も知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な〜んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片も北条さん狙い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや　西片は高木さんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.05,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いやいや 全然 違うから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあ 大人っぽさっていったらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やっぱ あれじゃねえかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“あれ”?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.52,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“あれ”って 何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,教えてよ  教えてくれよ 木村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“コーシー”だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ  それ コーヒーだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:27.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ああ  なんか今日 そんな気分でね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントに飲めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 苦いの苦手でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんなこと言ってられるのも  今のうちだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,前に 朝食で  母さんが出したコーヒー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:42.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おいしくはなかったが  飲めないほどじゃなかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.43,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺の大人っぽさにビビれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そして もう からかうなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,にがっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:50.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何だこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに すごい においが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やっぱり苦手なんじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  うまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんか この… 目の覚める感じがさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,飲まないの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:07.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,飲むけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ  西片 手汗かいてない?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,かいてないよ  これは缶についてた水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.21,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっ  そういえば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ネットで  “正しいコーヒーの味わい方”  って見たことあってね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“口の中で しばらく転がすと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,においが感じられて いい”って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ  こんなものを  口の中に しばらく置いとく?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ウソだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.02,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そういうデマを見たことあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,くそ… そんなふうに  からかえるのも今のうちだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,コーヒーを飲み干す俺に  ひれ伏すがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんなに苦手なら  買わなきゃいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや おいしくてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんも飲んだら  約束だから おごってあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,好きな物選んで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:04.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何にしよっかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,メ… メロンソーダ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おいしそう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,交換してあげよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:46.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 俺 コーヒー好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんとか飲みきった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,舌がビリビリする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,でも どうだ  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,メロンソーダ ひと口飲む
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや でも 欲しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,甘い物を飲みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ… じゃあ  せっかくだから もらおうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,間接キスだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.22,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,コーヒーの後味を楽しむかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:33.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,コーヒーを飲めても  別に大人っぽくないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:44.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,とっくに見抜かれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに 西片が大人っぽくなっても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.74,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私は頑張って からかうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:54.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ… あっ ちょ…   もう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.50,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そこは頑張らないでよ 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう 笑ってばっかで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.02,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,昨日も さんざんだった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日こそ 何か高木さんに  勝てるものはないか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:53.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あ  おはよう 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,一緒に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何だ  いつもと感じが違うような
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日 自転車は?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:12.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片と手つないで  学校行きたくて 置いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…と思う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,思わないよ 全然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,すぐこれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.05,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これでいけるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,実は 自転車…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って 今日 自転車じゃない理由  当てられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺の勝ちってのは どう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,昨日 帰り道で  チラッと言っていた あのセリフ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんかブレーキの利きが悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺は聞き逃してないのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こうも あっさり勝てるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,少し拍子抜けだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.45,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,答えは ブレ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,間違ったら  その時点で西片の負けだからね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:05.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,答えは?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もうちょっと あとで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:11.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そう
Comment: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.22,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こっちから行ってみない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:14.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,階段  自転車だと階段はムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,このルートを通るために?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,多分 それだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:20.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:38.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ここは慎重に もう少し考えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:44.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車ないと  いつもと違う道通れて 楽しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やはり 違うのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:54.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この道 近所の子供たちが  よく地面に絵とか描いてるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:56.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,例えばね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ほら  あったあった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けんぱ遊び やってみようっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.63,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けん ぱ  けん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.30,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けん ぱ  けん ぱ   けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんも  まだまだ お子ちゃまだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車ないと  けんぱ遊びできて ホント楽しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんは この道に けんぱ遊びの  落書きがあることを予想していた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車がなければ 自分も遊べる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.15,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いやいや　焦るな 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,間違ったら負けなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.74,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.20,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じっくり考えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.49,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.16,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん  この勝負  公平じゃない気がするんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:51.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:57.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だって 正解しても 高木さんが“違う”って言ったら 俺の負けになっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:02.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ  私 西片にはウソつかないから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.05,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,猫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こっちにもいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この道 猫多いんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.27,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おいおい  どうだ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.41,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん  答えを言ってもいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん  どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:29.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日 自転車ではなく  歩いて登校している理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ブレーキの故障
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:38.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,階段 けんぱ遊び  そして 猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:43.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車にはできないことに  意識を向けようとしたみたいだが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,少し やりすぎてしまったようだね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:53.02,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,昨日 思わず  口に出してしまった—ブレーキの違和感から 俺の思考を  遠ざけようとしているのが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.27,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,バレバレだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうだい  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,正解か 不正解か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:20:59.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,不正解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:09.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,正解は “なぜ私が自転車じゃないのか  その理由を当てようとして”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:13.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“あれこれ悩んでいる西片を  見たいから”でした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントだよ  西片の負け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:24.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺が勝負を  仕掛けるところから 既に…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,残念だったね  答え 2つも用意しといたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:32.31,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,2つ?  2つって…別の正解があるってこと?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:32.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう1この答えって 何だったの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片には当てられないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片の負けだし もういいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ  教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,さあね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.62,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,気になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.29,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,最初に言ったんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:00.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ なに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お… 教えてよ 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないわけないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないもん
